title: Power Outage Affects East Sioux Falls, Brandon
text:
Power Outage Affects East Sioux Falls, Brandon October 12, 2015, 7:07 AM SIOUX FALLS, SD - 
Xcel Energy says more than 3,000 customers are affected by a power outage. 
Customers east of Interstate 229 are affected, along with customers in Brandon and Garretson. 
Service is expected to be restored before 9 a.m. Â© 2015 KELOLAND TV. All Rights Reserved.
